text: Petra Walczewski (born 27 April 1968) is a road cyclist from Switzerland. She represented her nation at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Swiss female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Switzerland Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:1968 births
